I have only seen belly pans on deluxes and
double-doors. I have seen plenty of Kombi's that do
not have bellypans. SO42 Westfalias for example are
kombis that, is they were ordered with a pop-top, were
sunroof models. I have never seen a SO42 with belly
pans. 

